        <item>
            <title>《魔物猎人，荒野》支援跨平台游玩  PS5、XBOX、PC 版将同步开售</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/09/monster-hunter-wilds/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=monster-hunter-wilds</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/09/monster-hunter-wilds/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 07:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Monster Hunter Wilds]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[魔物猎人，荒野]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1241791</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>CAPCOM 于 2024 年夏季游戏节上正式公布《Monster Hunter Wilds》（魔物猎人，荒野）支援跨平台游玩，游戏将在 2025 年同步推出 PS5、XSX/S 及 PC 版本，并展示了全新大型魔物「沙海龙」。此次更新确立了玩家可以跨平台连线游玩，并在游戏选项中启用或禁用此功能。然而，该游戏并不支援跨平台存档，各平台的存档数据将独立管理。</p><p>CAPCOM 在最新推出的宣传影片中，展示《魔物猎人，荒野》游戏实机画面，并揭露了全新魔物「沙海龙」的特性。沙海龙可以在沙漠地形中自由穿梭，并以其体内分泌的黏液进行攻击。影片还展示了猎人在恶劣的环境中与各种魔物的激烈战斗，强调了游戏中环境对魔物行为的影响，以及玩家需要密切关注周围环境以进行狩猎。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241792" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cd49d3c1252511efbfff-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cd49d3c1252511efbfff-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/cd49d3c1252511efbfff.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h3><p>《魔物猎人，荒野》将深刻的故事与游戏无缝衔接，带给玩家沉浸式的体验。游戏中，玩家将在「天堑沙原」上与魔物群对峙，并深入探索这片充满神秘色彩的原野。在封禁之地的严酷环境中，玩家需要应对沙尘暴和雷击等自然现象，并与各种强大的魔物展开生死搏斗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241795" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/171781918227551_p297-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/171781918227551_p297-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/171781918227551_p297.jpeg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>支援跨平台游玩</h3><p>CAPCOM 确认，玩家将能够在 PS5、XSX/S 及 PC 平台之间跨平台连线游玩。虽然游戏支援跨平台连线，但不支援跨平台存档，各平台的存档数据将独立管理。因此，玩家无法在不同平台之间共享游戏进度和已购 DLC 等内容。</p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1241794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monsterhunterwildsps-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monsterhunterwildsps-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monsterhunterwildsps-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/monsterhunterwildsps.jpg 660w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></h3><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_70673"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oN_ngxW1Iu4?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/monster-hunter-wilds-crossplay-confirmed-alongside-new-trailer">IGN</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/monsterhunterwilds/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Monster Hunter Wilds 首段预告片【有片睇】新魔物 + 新坐骑 + 新玩法</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/09/monster-hunter-wilds/game-channel/">《魔物猎人，荒野》支援跨平台游玩  PS5、XBOX、PC 版将同步开售</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
